parameter_set_periods.notice_text:
Welcome to the study.

We will display important information throughout the study in this section.

Today we will talk about the interface, connect the Fitbit to your phone then link your Fitbit account to the study.

If you have questions please raise your hand.

The first week of the study is complete.

You will receive your first payment, the sum of the previous seven days, today by 5 pm from PayPal sent to your Chapman email address.

The way you earn money has changed.  Instead of earning a fixed amount each day, we will now pay you based number of Zone Minutes you and your partner accrue each day.

For more information press the help buttons (?) in each frame.

The way you earn money has changed.  Instead of paying you based number of Zone Minutes you and your partner accrue each day, you and your partner will earn a fixed amount for checking in each day.

For more information press the help buttons (?) in each frame.

The way you earn money has changed. You and your partner will no longer earn money for checking in each day.  However, if you continue to check in each day, you will be allowed to keep your Fitbit at the end fo the study.

For more information press the help buttons (?) in each frame.

Today is the last day of the study.

You will receive your final payment tomorrow.

Thank you for your participation!
